Updates a requirement in a composer.json file for a given skin or extension

Usage: mwdev --composer --skin BlueSky --package mediawiki/mediawiki-codesniffer --version 0.7.1
       mwdev --composer --extension MyExtension --package foo/somePackage --version ^1.2

--skins                         Run for all skins
--extensions                    Run for all extensions
--skin <skinName>               Run for the given skin
--extension <extensionName>     Run for the given extension
--package <packageName>         The composer package to work on
--version <versionNumber>       The version to change to
--from <versionNumber>          The version number to move from
--push                          Push a new draft change to Gerrit!
